WEBVTT

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:08.620
=Destiny of the General's Bride=

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:12.020
=Episode 24=

00:00:16.839 --> 00:00:20.000
Xiao Yun is indeed Your Lordship's son.

00:00:26.839 --> 00:00:29.079
I was Old General Xiao's most beloved.

00:00:29.359 --> 00:00:31.079
How could I not know
the truth behind it?

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:33.359
But Miss Qing Yan,

00:00:33.759 --> 00:00:36.560
do you think the Xiao family
are some ordinary household?

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:39.640
It's nothing but complicated.

00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:41.359
I only wish for Xiao Yun

00:00:41.359 --> 00:00:42.719
to receive better care

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:44.320
as the eldest son.

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:48.600
Don't you understand
my kind thought, Your Lordship?

00:00:51.759 --> 00:00:53.600
But I've never seen a mother

00:00:54.039 --> 00:00:56.159
plot to kill her own child.

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:58.600
Xiao Yun was on death row
for a grave crime.

00:00:59.439 --> 00:01:00.679
What punishment he received

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:02.119
was beyond my control.

00:01:03.399 --> 00:01:05.719
That means the warden abused his power.

00:01:06.079 --> 00:01:06.719
Your Lordship!

00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:07.680
Your Lordship!

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:10.519
It's all Grand Madam Xiao's doing.

00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:11.840
She had me use a hemp whip

00:01:12.120 --> 00:01:14.079
to get back at General Xiao double

00:01:14.120 --> 00:01:15.200
for what he did to Xiao Ye.

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:16.599
Yesterday,

00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:18.959
she even entered the cell with Xiao Ye

00:01:19.359 --> 00:01:21.000
and beat General Xiao!

00:01:26.159 --> 00:01:27.159
Xiao Ye!

00:01:35.959 --> 00:01:38.000
All these years,
you've been overbearing

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:40.560
by riding on my power

00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:42.560
and using my guilt.

00:01:43.319 --> 00:01:45.799
I didn't expect you knew all along

00:01:46.719 --> 00:01:48.799
you were posing as Xiao Yun.

00:01:55.319 --> 00:01:56.000
Why?

00:01:58.560 --> 00:01:59.840
Each of you

00:02:00.840 --> 00:02:02.359
starts blaming me, huh?

00:02:03.640 --> 00:02:04.280
That's right.

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:07.000
I am overbearing.

00:02:07.879 --> 00:02:09.759
But you, King of Xiling,
are no saint either.

00:02:12.039 --> 00:02:15.360
You said you feared
implicating him and his mother.

00:02:19.159 --> 00:02:20.000
What a joke!

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:23.960
To you,

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:27.199
your achievements come first.

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:31.800
If you truly loved Mo Mei,

00:02:33.479 --> 00:02:35.080
you would've given up everything

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:37.360
to spend the rest of your life with her.

00:02:38.439 --> 00:02:40.280
And things wouldn't
have come to this point!

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.199
Ye!

00:02:41.719 --> 00:02:42.520
Stop that nonsense!

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:43.319
I'm talking nonsense?

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:45.719
Mother.

00:02:46.919 --> 00:02:48.520
You're the one babbling nonsense here!

00:02:51.599 --> 00:02:52.879
I ever thought

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:56.199
I had a happy family.

00:02:57.039 --> 00:02:58.039
Until one day,

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:00.560
I found out that my mother

00:03:04.280 --> 00:03:06.240
was poisoning another woman.

00:03:08.759 --> 00:03:10.039
After that, you even made me

00:03:11.520 --> 00:03:13.680
pretend to be someone else
so as to avoid trouble.

00:03:13.919 --> 00:03:15.840
I did all this for your own sake!

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.240
You did it for your own sake!

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:21.199
Ever since you knew
you were in deep water,

00:03:22.759 --> 00:03:23.960
you made me imitate Xiao Yun,

00:03:24.800 --> 00:03:26.199
imitate the King of Xiling,

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:29.039
so everyone would think

00:03:29.960 --> 00:03:31.879
I was the King of Xiling's son.

00:03:32.479 --> 00:03:33.400
All these years,

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:36.439
I've always treated you like my own!

00:03:36.479 --> 00:03:37.639
I don't want that!

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:46.759
These years,

00:03:47.919 --> 00:03:49.520
I've constantly targeted Xiao Yun,

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:51.759
afraid people would expose

00:03:52.520 --> 00:03:54.199
that I'd usurped his place

00:03:55.719 --> 00:03:57.759
and claim I'd taken
such advantage of him.

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:00.800
But who ever truly thought of me?

00:04:08.479 --> 00:04:12.360
The one truly robbed of a life is me.

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:14.159
It's me!

00:04:15.719 --> 00:04:17.720
What about the life taken from Xiao Yun?

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:19.879
We just let it slide?

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:21.920
He deserved it.

00:04:22.959 --> 00:04:24.839
No one deserves your bullying.

00:04:25.399 --> 00:04:26.240
Xiao Ye.

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:28.279
You've done evil,

00:04:28.639 --> 00:04:30.079
so it's time to pay the price.

00:04:32.639 --> 00:04:33.759
At this point,

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:38.800
none of you has the right to judge me.

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:51.439
Ye!

00:04:58.800 --> 00:04:59.639
Ye!

00:05:00.319 --> 00:05:01.160
Ye!

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:03.240
Ye!

00:05:08.439 --> 00:05:10.480
I was deceived for twenty years!

00:05:13.879 --> 00:05:14.680
Guards!

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:19.000
Arrest Madam Xiao!

00:05:19.519 --> 00:05:21.439
Investigate all her crimes

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:23.720
and execute her accordingly!

00:05:25.639 --> 00:05:26.240
Qing Yan!

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:27.120
Don't come closer!

00:05:27.879 --> 00:05:28.720
No one come closer!

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:36.560
Xiao Yun, oh, Xiao Yun.

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.639
You think finding Qing Yan

00:05:38.639 --> 00:05:39.959
means you found true love?

00:05:40.879 --> 00:05:42.920
Your mother and father abandoned you.

00:05:43.879 --> 00:05:47.279
You're doomed to be forever alone.

00:05:48.079 --> 00:05:48.800
Let her go.

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:50.439
We can talk this out.

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:51.720
Don't come closer!

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:52.920
Come closer

00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:53.920
and I'll kill her!

00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:58.480
They've all backed off.

00:05:58.759 --> 00:06:00.319
Tell me what exactly you want.

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:06.560
I shouldn't have buried Qing Yan then.

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:09.480
I should've cut her
into a thousand pieces,

00:06:10.879 --> 00:06:13.000
so my Ye wouldn't end up this way.

00:06:15.519 --> 00:06:18.439
Let her go and we can talk.

00:06:20.319 --> 00:06:22.160
I want you
to pay with your life for Ye's death.

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:24.199
Will you?

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:27.560
Let her go

00:06:27.839 --> 00:06:29.199
and I'll spare your life.

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:30.160
How can I live

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:31.399
without Ye?

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:34.560
Su Man'er is pregnant.

00:06:35.759 --> 00:06:37.120
Xiao Ye still has a child.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:38.439
What did you say?

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:41.160
I said, Su Man'er is pregnant.

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:43.240
That's Xiao Ye's only bloodline.

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:47.399
Don't you dare lie to me!

00:06:48.480 --> 00:06:49.519
As if I didn't know

00:06:50.279 --> 00:06:52.560
you hate your sister and me
for hurting you.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.439
Considering how wicked you are,

00:06:54.879 --> 00:06:56.279
you'd kill her outright

00:06:56.759 --> 00:06:57.959
if you knew her whereabouts.

00:06:58.079 --> 00:06:59.600
As if you'd let her carry a child!

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:02.360
You evil woman.

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:05.600
You're still lying
even though you're dying.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:07.519
And yet this man

00:07:07.519 --> 00:07:09.319
is putting his life at risk for you.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:13.040
How laughable!

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:14.680
If you hadn't deceived Xiao Ye,

00:07:14.879 --> 00:07:17.000
making him believe there's no true love,

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:19.160
how would he end up like this?

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.120
I'll kill you!

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:28.399
Qing Yan!

00:07:30.600 --> 00:07:31.279
Take her!

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:50.439
If the heart is as steadfast
as the hairpiece,

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:54.199
the twain shall meet,
be it in heaven or on earth.

00:07:56.319 --> 00:07:58.000
I was so afraid you'd recognize me.

00:07:59.519 --> 00:08:01.319
I was also afraid you wouldn't.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:03.759
But both of us

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:07.399
are to meet in hell.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:10.399
As long as I'm with you,

00:08:12.840 --> 00:08:16.120
it doesn't matter where it is,
be it in heaven or the netherworld.

00:08:20.340 --> 00:08:24.620
♪You went left, I went right♪

00:08:24.620 --> 00:08:28.240
♪If we hadn't met,
there'd be nothing to seek♪

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:28.839
Hua.

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:31.560
No matter what you want to do

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:33.639
or what you want me to do,

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:35.720
I'll be your side,

00:08:36.240 --> 00:08:37.000
waiting for you.

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:40.559
However, on one condition.

00:08:42.279 --> 00:08:43.000
Can you

00:08:44.399 --> 00:08:45.480
stop disappearing on me?

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:48.540
♪Gentle longing flows into the river♪

00:08:48.540 --> 00:08:53.540
♪When dreams break,
we will guard each other still♪

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:04.399
Yun.

00:09:05.679 --> 00:09:06.759
How much do I matter

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:09.080
to you?

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.960
Even a weighing scale fails to measure that.

00:09:20.559 --> 00:09:21.639
You're the only one I want.

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:24.240
No matter what you look like.

00:09:26.759 --> 00:09:27.399
I promise.

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:30.039
After the show tomorrow,

00:09:30.840 --> 00:09:32.440
I won't push you away again.

00:09:37.399 --> 00:09:38.240
Miss Yu!

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:40.240
Miss Yu!

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.360
Miss Yu!

00:09:49.879 --> 00:09:51.320
Miss Yu!

00:09:52.860 --> 00:09:56.420
♪Love and hate poured
in a single jar of wine♪

00:09:56.420 --> 00:10:00.540
♪Whose heart does love truly claim♪

00:10:00.540 --> 00:10:04.300
♪Yet it yields to just one greeting♪

