we will guard each other still♪

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:17.159
By the oral decree of Princess Zhaoping,

00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:19.799
(Xiao Residence)
Madam Xiao committed countless evil deeds

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:22.240
and harmed innocent ladies.

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:25.240
She is ordered to build tombstones

00:10:25.240 --> 00:10:26.720
for the ones she harmed,

00:10:27.000 --> 00:10:28.799
which she will guard until death.

00:10:29.480 --> 00:10:32.200
Madam Zhang too did many evil deeds.

00:10:32.519 --> 00:10:34.919
Yet considering her sincere repentance

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:36.559
and atonement,

00:10:36.960 --> 00:10:39.519
she is ordered to sweep
the graves of the women

00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:41.679
on the 1st and 15th of every month.

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:44.759
Undaunted by power, Madam Qing Yan

00:10:44.960 --> 00:10:46.840
pled for justice for these women.

00:10:47.159 --> 00:10:48.759
Her loyalty and courage are commendable

00:10:49.039 --> 00:10:51.159
She is posthumously honored
with a noble title.

00:10:51.780 --> 00:10:54.440
(Xiao Residence)

00:10:54.440 --> 00:10:56.240
General Xiao is truly heartless.

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:57.840
It hasn't been long
since his wife's passing,

00:10:58.080 --> 00:10:59.320
and he's already marrying another.

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:02.519
I heard this marriage
was arranged by the palace.

00:11:02.960 --> 00:11:05.080
Even the King of Xiling
and Princess Zhaoping

00:11:05.279 --> 00:11:06.720
came to send him gifts.

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:07.919
But didn't Qing Yan

00:11:07.919 --> 00:11:09.200
save Princess Zhaoping's life?

00:11:09.240 --> 00:11:10.600
Doesn't that mean it was all in vain?

00:11:10.679 --> 00:11:11.720
How could she do this

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.039
This is my mother.

00:11:27.380 --> 00:11:29.000
(Memorial Tablet of Mother, Mo Mei)

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:30.159
(Memorial Tablet of Wife, Qing Yan)
And this is my late wife,

00:11:31.519 --> 00:11:32.200
Qing Yan.

00:11:38.759 --> 00:11:40.360
Greetings, Mother.

00:11:43.759 --> 00:11:44.879
Greetings, Sister.

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:47.279
May both of you

00:11:47.840 --> 00:11:51.440
bless my husband and me
with harmony and happiness.

00:11:53.159 --> 00:11:54.840
I, Su Hua, thank you.

00:12:32.120 --> 00:12:32.799
Hua.

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:39.799
Qing Yan is dead.

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:41.600
Su Hua is reborn.

00:12:42.919 --> 00:12:44.279
General Xiao, I look forward to

00:12:45.879 --> 00:12:46.759
our life together.

